fects of these drugs and in whom toxicity symptoms may be easily overlooked.', 'Moderate', 'pharmacodynamic', NULL, 'https://ddinter2.scbdd.com/server/interact/27172/', '', 'Mometasone furoate, Terbutaline, Budesonide, Mometasone, Epinephrine, Olodaterol, Fluticasone, Cromoglicic acid, Salbutamol, Orciprenaline, Pirbuterol, More', 'Tropicamide, Ephedrine, Ketorolac', 1767369485);
