h CYP450 3A4 inhibitors, particularly potent and moderate inhibitors (e.', 'Major', 'pharmacodynamic', NULL, 'https://ddinter2.scbdd.com/server/interact/27205/', '', 'Dextromethorphan, Clofedanol, Benzonatate, Pentoxyverine, Codeine', 'Caspofungin, Micafungin, Amphotericin B, Oteseconazole, Flucytosine, Anidulafungin', 1767369485);
